{"tid":60621,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖慎入]有無人知虹之玉點養?","createTime":"2016-12-30T14:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T05:04:00.000Z","uid":8351,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b06a18aaca96455622fb532bd24b74dfbae0a433","tid":60621,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"我買完返嚟突然發現<br />\n原來我唔知要點養<br />\neg.泥 水 肥料 etc<br />\n上過網查但覺得資料唔夠多<br />\n跪求各位大神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附上圖片多張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/224756_67cfda47df5f436b6acd3708fdc3f25c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F224756_67cfda47df5f436b6acd3708fdc3f25c.jpg&h=01d6d5aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/224828_bcd9ca921464798c59712a7f9450cd6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F224828_bcd9ca921464798c59712a7f9450cd6e.jpg&h=786e3e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n背面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR5UfVfW4pbBJY8mkYQwhtHjuq9KMwq57MteK4KPmDjAM?filename=uB4uu14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuB4uu14.jpg&h=56547910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭頂耶蘇光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPuqHiTecReaDa8XejnseNspvxBLUm1zgjr1e7r64xpGW?filename=CA0202M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCA0202M.jpg&h=b6fe5755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袋底無窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcZUNuXgQLFc5ev11oH8mX81L83xuXQivhY4tAM3aiDeX?filename=66u7101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66u7101.jpg&h=fce95b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後附上腦魔合照一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝定各位巴打新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ab9ff704ce98dd50fecd5d7d428370ec6ca6ec","tid":60621,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"Pish pish pish!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed9cde74df019587c01d576f05b5548395a94c2","tid":60621,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"我唔想佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cea681f26c3b4e612f2b86e38c96a0eb3d19dc","tid":60621,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"首先要有陽光？"},{"pid":"a60bac161c55331b0d267e331bb6058806e8372b","tid":60621,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先要有陽光？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每日都有掟佢出屋比太陽伯伯射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00393f2f7a861548d947a033b056819baacd6220","tid":60621,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9495893c81f6d8d39199cc8f